resources.description: Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and Agrovoc. This file contains 1, 378 semantic alignments to the FAO agricultural thesaurus.
Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and Eclas. This file contains 4, 122 semantic alignments to the thesaurus of the European Commission Library.
Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and Gemet. This file contains 1, 676 semantic alignments to the GEneral Multilingual Environmental Thesaurus.
Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and Unbis (United Nations Thesaurus). This file contains 2, 029 semantic alignments to the United Nations Thesaurus.

Distribution – Alignment – EuroVoc and Inspire. This file contains 119  semantic alignments to the Inspire themes or feature concept dictionary. These alignments are the result of an exercise carried  out outside the official framework of INSPIRE, and they have not been endorsed by the INSPIRE Maintenance and Implementation Group. As such, they must not be regarded as stating an official position of INSPIRE.

      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="bg">EuroVoc е многоезичен и мултидисциплинарен тезаурус, обхващащ терминологията от областите на дейност на Европейския съюз.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="es">EuroVoc es un tesauro multilingüe y multidisciplinario que abarca la terminología de los ámbitos de actividad de la Unión Europea.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="cs">EuroVoc je vícejazyčný polytematický tezaurus s terminologií oblastí, kterými se zabývá Evropská unie.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="da">EuroVoc er en flersproglig og tværfaglig tesaurus, der dækker terminologien inden for EU's aktivitetsområder.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="de">EuroVoc ist ein mehrsprachiger multidisziplinärer Thesaurus, der die Terminologie der Tätigkeitsbereiche der Europäischen Union abdeckt.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="el">Το EuroVoc είναι μια πολύγλωσση και πολυτομεακή συλλογή όρων που καλύπτει την ορολογία των διαφόρων τομέων δραστηριότητας της Ευρωπαϊκής Ένωσης.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="en">EuroVoc is a multilingual, multidisciplinary thesaurus covering the activities of the EU.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="et">EuroVoc on mitmekeelne erinevaid valdkondi hõlmav tesaurus, mis sisaldab Euroopa Liidu tegevusvaldkondi käsitlevat terminoloogiat.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="fr">EuroVoc est un thésaurus multilingue et multidisciplinaire couvrant la terminologie des domaines d'activité de l'Union européenne.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="hr">EuroVoc je višejezični i višepodručni pojmovnik koji obuhvaća djelatnosti EU-a.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="it">EuroVoc è un thesaurus multilingue e pluridisciplinare che comprende la terminologia dei settori d'attività dell'Unione europea.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="lv">“Eurovoc ir daudzvalodu un daudznozaru tēzaurs, kas aptver Eiropas Savienības darbības jomu terminoloģiju.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="lt">„EuroVoc“ – tai daugiakalbis ir daugiadalykis tezauras, kuriame pateikiama Europos Sąjungos veiklos sričių terminija.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="hu">Az Eurovoc olyan többnyelvű multidiszciplináris tezaurusz, amely az Európai Unió tevékenységi területeire vonatkozó lexikai egységeket fedi le.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="mt">EuroVoc hu teżawru multilingwi u multidixxiplinarju li jkopri t-terminoloġija fl-oqsma ta’ attività tal-Unjoni Ewropea.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="nl">EuroVoc is een meertalige en multidisciplinaire thesaurus die alle gebieden omvat waarop de Europese Unie actief is.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="pl">Eurovoc to wielojęzyczny, wszechstronny tezaurus obejmujący terminologię z zakresu poszczególnych obszarów działalności Unii Europejskiej.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="pt">O Eurovoc é um tesauro multilingue e multidisciplinar que integra a terminologia dos domínios de actividade da União Europeia.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="ro">Eurovoc este un tezaur multilingv şi multidisciplinar care acoperă terminologia domeniilor de activitate ale Uniunii Europene.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="sk">Eurovoc je viacjazyčný, multidisciplinárny tezaurus pokrývajúci terminológiu z oblastí činnosti Európskej únie.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="sl">Tezaver EuroVoc je večjezična multidisciplinarna terminološka zbirka s področij dejavnosti institucij Evropske unije.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="fi">Eurovoc on monikielinen ja monialainen tesaurus, joka kattaa Euroopan unionin kaikki toimialat.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="sv">Eurovoc är en flerspråkig och ämnesövergripande tesaurus för terminologin inom EU:s olika verksamhetsområden.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="mk">Евровок на Европската Унија е повеќејазичен, повеќедисциплинарен поимник меѓу чии корисници се Европскиот парламент.</dct:description>
      <!--Description, 1..*--><dct:description xml:lang="sr">EuroVoc је вишејезички, мултидисциплинарни тезаурус који покрива активности Европске уније (ЕУ).</dct:description>
